			</classificationInformation>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">Masterbatches are concentrated mixtures of pigments, additives, or modifiers that are used to color or enhance the properties of plastics, rubber, or other materials during the manufacturing process. They are widely used in industries like packaging, automotive, construction, and more. Masterbatch is a blend of pigments, additives, and polymer materials (carrier resin). It is used as a chemical ingredient to enhance the properties of plastics and impart shades of color.</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">色母粒是颜料、添加剂或改性剂的浓缩混合物，在生产过程中用于着色或增强塑料、橡胶或其他材料的性能。它们广泛应用于包装、汽车、建筑等行业。色母粒是颜料、添加剂和聚合物材料（载体树脂）的混合物。它是一种化学成分，用于提高塑料的性能并赋予颜色深浅。</common:generalComment>
